de.ddkfm.util.transform

Class Microcode

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ddkfm.util.transform.Microcode

  • public class Microcode
extends java.lang.Object
    The Microcode class represents the Microcode for the decoder in the simulation The Microcode contains 16 instructions
    See Also:
    By default the instructions will be loaded with default instructions
